              {
                "kind": "text",
                "text": "About the verse \"It is in love that we are made, in love we disappear\"."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "kind": "lineBreak"
          },
          {
            "kind": "lineBreak"
          },
          {
            "kind": "text",
            "id": "2",
            "tokens": [
              {
                "kind": "text",
                "text": "That's just a journalistic reportage of the process. We are made in love and in love we disappear. But that love is not the romantic love, it's the impersonal, benign activity that governs creation and destruction."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "kind": "lineBreak"
          },
          {
            "kind": "lineBreak"
          }
        ]
      },
