            "id": "1",
            "tokens": [
              {
                "kind": "text",
                "text": "About the relation between John Simon (producer of the album \"Songs Of L. Cohen\") and Leonard"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "kind": "lineBreak"
          },
          {
            "kind": "lineBreak"
          },
          {
            "kind": "text",
            "id": "2",
            "tokens": [
              {
                "kind": "text",
                "text": "We did have a falling out over the song Suzanne. He wanted a heavy piano syncopated and maybe drums and I didn't want drums on any of my songs, so that was a bone of contention. Also, he was ready to substitute this heavy chordal structure under the song to give it forward movement and I didn't like that."
              }
            ]
          },
